Lords & Ladles - Series 1, Episode 2




Tullynally Castle, Co. Westmeath

This 120 room aging mansion is home to Thomas Pakenham, Lord Longford, a passionate gardener and author of "Meetings with Remarkable Trees", who has filled the estate with exotic plants from his world travels. This ancestral home of Lord and Lady Longford is the largest house in Ireland that is in private ownership.



Original Air Date: 14-Jun-2015



Capper's Note: This REPACK fixes the audio pops that were heard in the original
